dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.bswmoduletemplate.bswinterfaces

Interface IBswModuleClientServerEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IReferrable

    public interface IBswModuleClientServerEntry
extends IEntity, IReferrable
    IBswModuleClientServerEntry: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents a single API entry into the BSW module or cluster that has the ability to be called in client-server fashion via the BSW Scheduler. In this regard it is more special than BswModuleEntry and can be seen as a wrapper around the BswModuleEntry to which it refers (property encapsulatedEntry).
